\id EPH - Abureni
\h E̠fi̠so̠s
\toc3 E̠fi̠s
\toc2 E̠fi̠so̠s
\toc1 A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m A̠nwunom E̠fi̠so̠s Bho̠
\mt2 A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m
\mt1 A̠nwunom E̠fi̠so̠s
\mt2 Bho̠
\imt1 Otighom
\ip Apo̠l age̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire onon ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na aro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli d̠a̠ A̠rom, sa̠ i̠na aru̠ru̠an agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠d̠ire bho̠ ta̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo raso̠si̠. Onon bo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ipa̠n ra̠d̠ire ya̠ Apo̠l age̠ bho̠. A̠d̠ire wa̠ i̠na age̠ agi̠o̠m ogbo E̠fi̠so̠s bho̠ na̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ e̠kal ali̠gam a̠ruzu, bo̠d̠o̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠ d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠. I̠na afi̠ri̠ma ma̠ Atai̠si̠ko̠s ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ akparame̠ni̠ sa̠ ta̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ raso̠si̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esele obha̠ bho̠. Apo̠l ake̠ ma̠ a̠duom d̠o̠yo̠ sekina̠ na̠ okpon od̠ighom d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ogir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gir a̠mutiom i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Sa̠ Apo̠l a̠ru d̠a̠ amu̠m onon, wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tenemeni sa̠ na̠ a̠nwe ale̠m ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠. I̠na a̠kunugiom agba onon na̠ aghi̠m wa̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠, d̠a̠ obhel bho̠ Witenemeni bho̠ ta̠ ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠karabh bho̠. Apo̠l agba a̠mutiom i̠se̠n ma̠a̠, i̠yar ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ onwuna̠ asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an, ezin bho̠ e̠gham d̠i̠yar ola̠ owia̠n a̠limon i̠karabh. I̠na agba a̠mutiom i̠di̠ar ilologia̠n ya̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ o̠wo̠l oten Akrai̠st, sa̠ agba ma̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ ma̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ ozu o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠, na̠ otu a̠siseiny, na̠ ani̠ erogh, na̠ o̠ni̠ e̠gham. Eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ eleriom ezin od̠igh onin, sa̠ na̠ eleriom ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ agba ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ eb̠la̠ ragba iyed̠i a̠gir gha̠n. D̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ d̠i̠yar, i̠yar owia̠n o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ omula̠ u̠man, o̠gho̠r i̠gho̠r, a̠fugh i̠te̠i̠, egbogbo ologi, i̠gam, na̠ igurumia̠n ologi. Ezin bho̠, i̠nye̠n o̠kpo̠ ya̠ na̠ ekigima̠ ma̠ od̠igh onin d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠. Apo̠l a̠kunugiom a̠d̠ire bho̠ na̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ ola̠ obhin orugh a̠ma̠rugh ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st, ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh eghun otu, na̠ ogir, na̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ obhin o̠mara o̠kparame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠.
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠
\io1 I̠to̠to̠gi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ itenemeni ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ bho̠ \ior (1:2-21)\ior*
\io1 E̠wo̠gi̠na Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ \ior (3:1-21)\ior*
\io1 A̠ma̠rugh ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom \ior (4:1—5:20)\ior*
\io1 A̠ghisia̠n ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠ \ior (5:21; 6:9)\ior*
\io1 E̠gham ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠ na̠ i̠karabh \ior (6:10-24)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Ipeleguma̠
\p 
\v 1 Ami̠ Apo̠l, wa̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠ten o̠ni̠ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st bho̠, na̠ age̠ na̠ a̠ruom a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ E̠fi̠so̠s, na̠ ogbo id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s.
\p 
\v 2 E̠no̠gho̠man na̠ ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin.
\s1 Itutumeni ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 3 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ itutumeni d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠doni i̠yar d̠a̠ Akrai̠st.
\v 4 Ezin bho̠ i̠na aso̠n i̠yar d̠a̠ Akrai̠st kisa̠ i̠na ale̠m e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom e̠b̠ab̠ala, orugh a̠ma̠rugh ola̠ abar ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m i̠yar ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 5 D̠a̠ etula̠n d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ato̠ a̠guri ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st obhin i̠yar ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠,
\v 6 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ otutumeni i̠na d̠a̠ ibom e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ ibom e̠no̠gho̠man na̠ e̠wo̠l d̠a̠ Wetula̠n bho̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠yar bho̠.
\v 7 D̠a̠ ebula̠ Akrai̠st sa̠ i̠yar u̠te̠i̠ itenemeni wa̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ alu̠kpe̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ u̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠i̠yar, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ibom e̠no̠gho̠man d̠o̠yo̠,
\v 8 ya̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ i̠yar a̠muzoghod̠i d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere eloghom abar na̠ amu̠gho̠nyan,
\v 9 ma̠ i̠yar ologhom e̠wo̠gi̠na i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠ isora̠n na̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠walama d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ i̠na ato̠ d̠a̠ Akrai̠st bho̠,
\v 10 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠walama d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠, ma̠ otulugi eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ Akrai̠st, d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny na̠ d̠a̠ a̠de onon.
\p 
\v 11 D̠a̠ ebula̠ Akrai̠st nyen, sa̠ u̠so̠n i̠yar ma̠ id̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a, ma̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ od̠ia̠ o̠to̠ oguri bho̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠sora̠n d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,
\v 12 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ya̠ u̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠pu̠r ogbo ya̠ na̠ eb̠em ologi d̠a̠ Akrai̠st bho̠ ta̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ itutumeni isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 13 D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠ sa̠ inyin u̠mu̠gho̠n nyen a̠ga̠i O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ oten d̠inyin, wa̠ inyin ud̠umom sa̠ u̠tu̠n o̠ku̠a unigha̠ inyin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ elegh, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ugua̠n bho̠,
\v 14 wa̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ ma̠ ogua̠n bho̠ ma̠a̠, i̠yar ta̠ od̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a d̠i̠yar bho̠, tu̠tu̠n i̠na ta̠ tenemeni ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ aman, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠ itutumeni d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠.
\s1 A̠siseiny ta̠ Apo̠l
\p 
\v 15 D̠a̠ ebul abar onon, na̠ o̠gba nyen onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ wa̠ inyin unwuna̠ ugboloma̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ etula̠n wa̠ inyin unwuna̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 16 O̠ku̠a sa̠ ami̠ ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠n ebula̠ inyin onigha̠ gha̠n ali̠se̠bh ma̠ igiel ami̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an igboloma̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠siseiny d̠ami̠,
\v 17 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, O̠we̠de̠ isosorogia̠n bho̠, ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin E̠mu̠gh eloghom abar na̠ aghi̠m ya̠ o̠mar ologhom o̠yo̠,
\v 18 na̠ okperon ologi d̠inyin ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar wa̠ i̠na atu̠n a̠bhelegi inyin bho̠, na̠ a̠b̠utu e̠li̠la ya̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gua̠n anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,
\v 19 sekina̠ ibom a̠limon d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ abar ola̠ obhin o̠tu̠o̠m o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, ya̠ i̠ro̠ inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ id̠umom bho̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠mi̠ a̠limon ogir agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,
\v 20 wa̠ i̠na a̠gir d̠a̠ ob̠eton Akrai̠st d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, sa̠ ari̠lo̠me̠ni̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny,
\v 21 a̠peleni ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠ a̠dila̠de na̠ a̠limon na̠ i̠to̠, sekina̠ kerekere a̠d̠ien ola̠ uloghom, i̠se̠n d̠a̠ amu̠m onon sekina̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠, nyen.
\v 22 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠bhin kabar kabar a̠guri d̠a̠ ekpukpu ta̠ Akrai̠st, sa̠ ato̠ ma̠a̠ i̠na we̠mu̠ eb̠la̠ i̠d̠i̠ar d̠a̠ ebula̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠,
\v 23 wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, wa̠ a̠muzo na̠ i̠na bho̠, wa̠ a̠muzo ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠d̠i̠ar bho̠.
\c 2
\s1 O̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ omugh od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um
\p 
\v 1 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ imumugh d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ ebula̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ na̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin.
\v 2 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, inyin u̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar e̠mara̠nwunom onon, ya̠ izuzua̠n a̠limon ta̠ Eru bho̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠rileghom ra̠limon d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny bho̠. I̠na e̠mu̠gh wa̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠rileghom ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 3 I̠ye̠ a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ eb̠la̠ i̠yar na̠ od̠ia̠ orugh otenemeni nyen, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ ipulupul ozu, sa̠ i̠yar u̠tu̠o̠no̠m gha̠n ebhiroma̠ ipulupul ozu na̠ iya̠ rologi d̠i̠yar ipuru bho̠. Sa̠ d̠a̠ e̠d̠o̠lo̠gho̠ma d̠a̠ i̠yar bho̠, sa̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ ogbika̠ d̠a̠ i̠gam ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ipa̠n ogbo.
\v 4 Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠muzo na̠ okpon igbirigbir bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ibom etula̠n ya̠ i̠na a̠tula̠n i̠yar bho̠,
\v 5 d̠a̠ igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ ma̠ imumugh d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ ebula̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ i̠yar a̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ Akrai̠st. Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ kisa̠ i̠yar uten.
\v 6 Sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠b̠eton i̠yar na̠ Akrai̠st ari̠lo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ a̠risisi ote̠nai̠ny na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, d̠a̠ ebula̠ od̠ighonin na̠ Akrai̠st,
\v 7 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠leriom amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠ ma̠ ibom e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gba o̠ro̠d̠o̠ bho̠ na̠ ib̠eb̠i ogir d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠yar ogbo ya̠ od̠i na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s bho̠.
\v 8 Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ inyin u̠wo̠l d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ uten, inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠, onon bha̠ enigha̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 9 Na̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠gir agu̠o̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠bhin are̠ma.
\v 10 Ezin bho̠, i̠yar ogir agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠ u̠le̠m d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s ma̠ ogir ib̠eb̠i rogir ya̠ i̠na na̠ ato̠ a̠guri, ma̠ i̠yar okpon o̠ku̠a ogir.
\s1 Eb̠la̠ A̠nwunom onin d̠a̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 11 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu d̠a̠ imitia̠n, sa̠ ogbo A̠zu ya̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠ awa na̠ otia̠ ma̠ ipo bho̠, ibhelegi inyin ma̠ ogbo ya̠ otia̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ipo, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ogir agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ipulupul bho̠.
\v 12 Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ obhel bho̠, inyin usia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st, inyin u̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun Izre̠l, u̠wal ani̠ d̠o̠ inyin o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ri̠zo̠ na̠ rogua̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, eb̠em ologi na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ inyin, inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom ya̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar egboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 13 Ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n, d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, inyin ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ esi egbeiny bho̠, na̠ obhin otueneni, d̠a̠ o̠wo̠l oten i̠ko̠l omugh ta̠ Akrai̠st.
\v 14 Ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ bha̠ ekima̠ d̠i̠yar, wa̠ a̠bhin i̠yar a̠guri onin bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin omugh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠b̠ogion e̠b̠agh wa̠ abagi̠o̠n i̠yar a̠guri ma̠ ogbo ologi̠an a̠d̠ien bho̠.
\v 15 I̠na a̠gbogion oloko i̠to̠to̠gi̠ a̠ma̠rugh bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ onwe o̠le̠m i̠wal rebhugh bho̠ otenemeni onin a̠nwunom iya̠ o̠yo̠, ya̠ ibhon ipu ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠ro̠ bho̠, omutiom ekima̠.
\v 16 D̠a̠ egbika̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠, sa̠ Akrai̠st a̠tulugi ma̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ onin d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠kunugiom o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien wa̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠i̠yar bho̠.
\v 17 Sa̠ Akrai̠st a̠ru ra̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ekima̠ bho̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu bho̠, ya̠ isigima̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ na̠ i̠yar a̠nwunom A̠zu, ya̠ itua̠n A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 18 I̠se̠n bha̠ i̠wal rekun bho̠ ta̠ e̠wo̠l d̠o̠yo̠, ebhin d̠a̠ onin E̠mu̠gh bho̠ e̠te̠i̠ O̠we̠d̠e̠ bho̠.
\p 
\v 19 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, inyin bo̠ mu̠ ma̠ isuloma̠ ya̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun, ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ oten anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ onin na̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, d̠a̠ eghun otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,
\v 20 ya̠ ulo d̠a̠ anyu̠ o̠de̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ sekina̠ a̠riwil bho̠, wa̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s na̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ o̠gbi̠o̠ma e̠ko̠ otu bho̠.
\v 21 D̠a̠ o̠yo̠ sa̠ eb̠la̠ otu bho̠ a̠tulugia̠n a̠ten onin, sa̠ abu̠gh a̠ten otupp ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.
\v 22 D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠, sa̠ ulo inyin utulugi nyen, utenemeni ma̠ otu ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh.
\c 3
\s1 Ogir wa̠ unigha̠ ma̠ Apo̠l ogir // ogboloma̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ // iya̠ A̠zu bho̠
\p 
\v 1 Onon abar wa̠ ami̠ Apo̠l, o̠ni̠ ikoli ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu bho̠, na̠ atu̠n na̠ a̠siseiny na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠.
\v 2 Ami̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ na̠ o̠gba onigha̠ inyin i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ aghu̠ame̠ni̠ ami̠ ma̠ ogir ogboloma̠ inyin bho̠.
\v 3 Uleriom ami̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar e̠wo̠gina ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ age̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠kara a̠gboloma̠ bho̠,
\v 4 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ orue osen o̠mu̠gho̠nyan i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ iloghom igboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar e̠wo̠gi̠na ta̠ Akrai̠st,
\v 5 ya̠ uleriom d̠o̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ramu̠m, ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n na̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠mutiom a̠leriom ogbo ogir na̠ a̠riwil d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ inigha̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠awa ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 6 E̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠ bha̠, ta̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ A̠zu ta̠ ed̠igh na̠ Ogbo A̠zu bho̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ id̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a, sa̠ awa ta̠ ed̠igh onin e̠ru̠gi̠an ogua̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s.
\v 7 Ami̠ iru ra̠ iten o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ agba ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ bho̠, wa̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠limon ogir d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mite bho̠.
\v 8 Ami̠ i̠ki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ unigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon obhin o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba onigha̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu bho̠, d̠a̠ e̠no̠gho̠man ya̠ imuzo d̠a̠ Akrai̠st bho̠.
\v 9 Sa̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠mar eloghom kabar kabar, d̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ilologia̠n na̠ i̠d̠i̠ar e̠wo̠gi̠na̠ id̠ud̠ul ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ ale̠m eb̠la̠ i̠d̠i̠ar bho̠,
\v 10 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠se̠n, ta̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ a̠leriom ogbo irileghom na̠ a̠limon ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny bho̠, ma̠ a̠d̠izo re̠kal eloghom abar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 11 I̠na atu̠n ebula̠ i̠walama id̠ud̠ul d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ramu̠m bho̠ a̠muzughod̠iom d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar,
\v 12 wa̠ i̠yar ubhin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ u̠te̠i̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi ola̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ omutuma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 13 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ologi d̠inyin odugh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠din inyin na̠ abi̠gh bho̠, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ itum d̠inyin bho̠.
\s1 Ologhom etula̠n ta̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 14 Onon ezin bho̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n O̠we̠de̠ bho̠,
\v 15 wa̠ u̠wo̠l ughol a̠d̠ien eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ re̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠de bho̠,
\v 16 ma̠a̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ ibom a̠b̠utu e̠no̠gho̠man isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠, awo̠l d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠limon ya̠ ta̠ e̠ghu̠ame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin,
\v 17 ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, sa̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠zu̠ o̠mara, o̠ro̠ gigiribh d̠a̠ etula̠n d̠o̠yo̠,
\v 18 b̠o̠ka̠ inyin od̠igh na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ o̠mar o̠mu̠gho̠nyan e̠re̠ghe̠, na̠ eweghe, na̠ e̠gi̠o̠m anyu̠, na̠ ekud̠um
\v 19 etula̠n ta̠ Akrai̠st wa̠ ob̠ur d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan o̠man bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ omuzo na̠ ado̠l ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal.
\p 
\v 20 I̠na wa̠ na̠ a̠rue na̠ a̠gir na̠ a̠peleni ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar na̠ opuru bho̠ na̠ iya̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠limon d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠gir d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar bho̠,
\v 21 a̠bhin itutumeni d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ i̠na bho̠ sekina̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, ad̠u̠a ma̠ amu̠m a̠ten amu̠m tu̠tu̠n ka̠ id̠ud̠ul. Aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.
\c 4
\s1 Od̠igh onin d̠a̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ikoli d̠a̠ ebula̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, na̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin ma̠ orugh a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ isora̠n agu̠o̠ ubhin ubhelegi inyin bho̠,
\v 2 d̠a̠ ibom o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu, na̠ ekima̠, na̠ a̠ma̠ne ya̠ odi ta̠ a̠ne ma̠ odi d̠a̠ ebula̠ etula̠n.
\v 3 Iwia̠ne ma̠ o̠ro̠ onin d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ekima̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ akpu̠o̠m inyin bho̠.
\v 4 Onin ozu na̠ onin E̠mu̠gh od̠i, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ubhelegi inyin nyen ra̠ ud̠ighom d̠a̠ onin eb̠em ologi bho̠,
\v 5 onin Wa̠nwuna̠, onin ologi ima̠ra̠, onin owura̠mu̠m,
\v 6 onin A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ O̠we̠de̠ ta̠ eb̠la̠ i̠yar, wa̠ a̠pu kabar kabar bho̠, sa̠ na̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠gir eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠yar.
\p 
\v 7 Ya̠a̠, Akrai̠st a̠nigha̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ i̠yar enigha̠ ya̠ o̠ni̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin a̠gir e̠kal ogir d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 8 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠,
\q1 “Ogiel bho̠ i̠na a̠bhun d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠,
\q2 sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ikoli e̠gham bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠.”
\p 
\v 9 I̠se̠n ka̠ “I̠na a̠bhun,” ka̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ eka̠, a̠sigimeni ma̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠a̠, i̠na a̠sor d̠a̠ agba wa̠ ade̠bh a̠pu d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠?
\v 10 I̠na wa̠ a̠sor bho̠ bha̠ uwa̠ a̠bhun bho̠ a̠pel eb̠la̠ re̠nai̠ny bho̠ nyen, ma̠ omuzo eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠.
\v 11 I̠na bha̠ wa̠ aso̠n idi ma̠ ogbogir, idi a̠riwil, idi i̠gba ma̠ asu̠gbagba, idi ikponom ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠,
\v 12 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ghu̠ame̠ni̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ ogir olo ozu ta̠ Akrai̠st obhuneni bho̠,
\v 13 tu̠tu̠n ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ a̠dila̠de ola̠ eb̠la̠ i̠yar ta̠ oten onin d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, o̠mar ologhom O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ o̠mar od̠igh e̠mu̠ olegha̠n ka̠ Akrai̠st.
\v 14 Sa̠ i̠yar ko o̠ro̠ mu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny, iya̠ ipoka̠na̠n amu̠m na̠ eb̠oroghom, na̠ a̠bhin na̠ agi̠ ma̠ ebha̠ na̠ enen d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere oghur atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, na̠ i̠le̠ge̠ na̠ ikoiny ogbo ya̠ na̠ egon ogelemeni a̠nwunom.
\v 15 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ i̠yar obhin d̠a̠ etula̠n o̠gba ma̠ iya̠ a̠ga̠i bho̠, sa̠ i̠yar ta̠ obhobh d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal o̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st we̠mu̠ bho̠.
\v 16 Ad̠u̠a d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ u̠tu̠lu̠gi̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠risisi ozu bho̠ na̠ id̠id̠igh uguri ma̠ onin, sa̠ esi i̠se̠ na̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ u̠to̠ unigha̠ i̠na ma̠ ogir bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ozu bho̠ a̠bhobh, aghu̠a, a̠muzo na̠ etula̠n.
\s1 Omom A̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ Akrai̠st
\p 
\v 17 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, o̠ni̠ ko orugh mu ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu na̠ erugh bho̠, ya̠ na̠ ebhin agu̠o̠ awa eb̠em ologi o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an.
\v 18 Awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar, ma̠ ola̠ awa na̠ esigima̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠. Ezin bho̠, awa iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i abar, d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠kparakpar ologi d̠awa.
\v 19 Awa inwuna̠ mu ma̠ igbiriri ozu, ma̠ ola̠ awa na̠ eb̠eton a̠ruzu d̠awa enigha̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere i̠karabh, na̠ a̠ma̠rugh o̠ku̠ku̠.
\v 20 Ya̠a̠, i̠nye̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin u̠tu̠ghan ugboloma̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠ d̠o̠,
\v 21 ku̠gba ma̠a̠, inyin o̠mar o̠mu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin a̠gia̠ga̠i ya̠ od̠i na̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠,
\v 22 bha̠ i̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ ado̠l ugba̠iny o̠ni̠ wa̠ obhon d̠o̠ bho̠ ma̠ erobh, ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ igelemeni iru bho̠.
\v 23 E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠nwe ma̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠inyin a̠tenemeni ma̠ imom,
\v 24 ma̠ erugh a̠ma̠rugh emobh o̠ni̠ ola̠ ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar bho̠ i̠gu̠b̠an ita̠ A̠zib̠a̠, d̠a̠ a̠ga̠i e̠b̠ab̠ala, na̠ igielake̠.
\p 
\v 25 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ o̠gba igunugha̠, ya̠a̠ odi agba ma̠ iya̠gia̠ga̠i a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ i̠yar onin d̠a̠ Akrai̠st.
\v 26 Inyin ta̠ orue o̠gam i̠gam, ya̠a̠ i̠gam bho̠ od̠ighi d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ ogir i̠karabh. I̠gam bho̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ tu̠tu̠n ogogo bho̠ ta̠ a̠sor.
\v 27 O̠ni̠ ko onigha̠ ma̠ Eru bho̠ ma̠ e̠ti̠ti̠gha.
\v 28 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rugh ado̠l a̠b̠igh ob̠igh mu, ya̠a̠ a̠bhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ akparame̠ni̠ a̠gir ogir ola̠ asu̠o̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ abar ola̠ onigha̠ ani̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠dila̠de bho̠ na̠ a̠puru ma̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠.
\v 29 I̠karabh a̠fugh omite d̠o̠ d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ d̠inyin. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i abar ola̠ ta̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ ed̠igh asu̠o̠ enigha̠ awa.
\v 30 O̠ni̠ ko od̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh i̠ku̠nu̠, i̠na wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠bhin na̠ a̠lelegi ma̠a̠ inyin iya̠ o̠yo̠ bho̠, na̠ oleriom ma̠a̠ inyin ta̠ oten d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ itenemeni bho̠.
\v 31 I̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ igurumia̠n ologi, na̠ ibom i̠gam, na̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠, izul o̠te̠i̠ abar onyen, na̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠, na̠ ado̠l o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien, sekina̠ eghir ologi d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠inyin.
\v 32 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ odi alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, odi a̠kpon odi ma̠ igbirigbir, odi a̠kpon i̠karabh ta̠ odi asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien, ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠n ebula̠ Akrai̠st a̠kpon i̠karabh d̠inyin asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien bho̠.
\c 5
\s1 Orugh d̠a̠ E̠b̠alab̠al
\p 
\v 1 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠ta ma̠ ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny ed̠ighologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\v 2 Irughe ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh etula̠n agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st a̠tula̠n i̠yar bho̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ abar alu̠kpe̠, ola̠ u̠kpe̠ unigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ a̠bhur ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠.
\v 3 Agu̠o̠ inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, odi o̠ni̠ inyin na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ na̠ a̠pesi ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ipesi, bo̠d̠o̠ na̠ a̠kori ma̠ i̠di̠ar na̠ a̠bhin. A̠ghud̠um i̠nye̠n ibhon d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ orugh.
\v 4 Bo̠d̠o̠ osenegi isenegi, ofugh a̠fugh iya̠ i̠te̠i̠, bo̠d̠o̠ okue ikue ya̠ osora̠n d̠o̠. Ado̠l i̠nye̠n ibhon d̠o̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ i̠se̠bhe̠ ma̠ ali̠se̠bh.
\v 5 Iloghome ma̠a̠, od̠e ma̠ e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ opesipesi, bo̠d̠o̠ okorikori (wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠l ma̠ eru bho̠), ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠de onwuna̠ e̠ma ta̠ Akrai̠st na̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\p 
\v 6 O̠ni̠ ko oma̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ obhin ibhelebhel o̠nu̠ oru ra̠ ogelemeni inyin. Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠din o̠kpo̠ ya̠ o̠ko̠no̠n agam ibom i̠gam a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ bho̠.
\v 7 O̠ni̠ ko od̠igh awa ma̠ egir a̠d̠ien i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ awa na̠ egir bho̠.
\v 8 Ezin bho̠, obhel aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin u̠ro̠ d̠a̠ azi̠m, ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n inyin na̠ oten a̠nwunom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al bho̠, bha̠, irughe ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ i̠gu̠b̠an ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al.
\v 9 Ezin bho̠, e̠b̠alab̠al onon wa̠ od̠i na̠ inyin bho̠, na̠ amu̠ na̠ a̠mutiom ib̠eb̠i, na̠ igielake̠, na̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i,
\v 10 ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ owia̠n ogir ya̠ i̠kpe̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 11 O̠ni̠ ko od̠igh ani̠ ma̠ egir i̠d̠i̠ar obhobho i̠kpo̠ i̠ye̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ azi̠m bho̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ i̠gba ma̠ emutiom agu̠o̠ igurom i̠te̠i̠.
\v 12 O̠kpo̠ i̠ye̠ ya̠ awa na̠ egir d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠, iya̠ ari̠ghe̠l nyen ma̠ ofugh ogboloma̠.
\v 13 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ umutiom eb̠la̠ o̠kpo̠ i̠ye̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al, sa̠ ta̠ ologhom agu̠o̠ obhin od̠i.
\v 14 Ezin bho̠ e̠b̠alab̠al na̠ a̠leriom kabar kabar, agu̠o̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠,
\q1 “B̠etina̠ d̠a̠ adi̠la d̠oyom,
\q2 b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh,
\q2 sa̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam amu̠gho̠nyan.”
\s1 Orugh d̠a̠ a̠limon E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠
\p 
\v 15 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠ ikpona̠, o̠ni̠ ko orugh agu̠o̠ rema̠ a̠nwunom, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ iloghodi̠ar a̠nwunom.
\v 16 I̠mare̠ ma̠ egir i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ inyin ogir d̠a̠ obhel bho̠, ezin bho̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠n i̠karabh.
\v 17 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, o̠ni̠ ko o̠ro̠ ma̠ rema̠, ya̠a̠ iwia̠ne ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 18 O̠ni̠ ko o̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min e̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ ta̠ epuru inyin, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠ye̠me̠ni̠ inyin. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠muzo d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin.
\v 19 Ibhine ma̠ raso̠r ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, na̠ raso̠r ya̠ a̠nwunom ima̠ra̠, na̠ raso̠r ya̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, ma̠ e̠mo̠r d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin, ma̠ etutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin.
\v 20 I̠se̠bhe̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ kigiel kigiel ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar, d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st.
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ Ani̠ na̠ Owolom
\p 
\v 21 Odi a̠zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi d̠a̠ ebula̠ oghila̠n Akrai̠st.
\v 22 Inyin anwani̠, izuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠siwolom d̠inyin, ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ ogir na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.
\v 23 Ezin bho̠, owolom we̠mu̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st aro̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ na̠ Witenemeni aso̠si̠ bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\v 24 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠, anwani̠ eka̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ a̠siwolom d̠awa d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar.
\v 25 Inyin a̠siwolom, itula̠ne ma̠ anwani̠ d̠inyin, ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ Akrai̠st a̠tula̠n aso̠si̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ a̠dinom.
\v 26 I̠na a̠gir o̠ku̠a b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na a̠bhin o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠wur amu̠m ma̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.
\v 27 Akrai̠st a̠gir o̠ko̠no̠n b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ aso̠si̠ ola̠ edim, ola̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ bebina̠ abar ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m, bo̠d̠o̠ ipa̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ ola̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ o̠pi̠e̠.
\v 28 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ a̠siwolom e̠kpe̠ ma̠ otula̠n anwani̠ d̠awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa itula̠n a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠. I̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠tula̠n ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, bha̠ a̠tula̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ nyen.
\v 29 Ezin bho̠, bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ asu̠a ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ amar na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n na̠ a̠kponom ozu d̠o̠yo̠, onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ Akrai̠st na̠ a̠gir na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠,
\v 30 ezin bho̠ i̠yar a̠risisi ozu d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 31 Onin agu̠o̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Olobho̠ro̠ni̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ akpabhan ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠wal awa ta̠ eten onin ozu.\x - \xo 5:31 \xt Ob̠et 2:24\x*”
\v 32 Onon obom e̠wo̠gi̠na, ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st na̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠.
\v 33 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, id̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ inyin ta̠ a̠tula̠n ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠tula̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ani̠ a̠zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ owolom d̠o̠yo̠.
\c 6
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny na̠ ronweni na̠ ro̠we̠de̠
\p 
\v 1 I̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny i̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin u̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, onon agu̠o̠ akpe̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠.
\v 2 “Izuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin.\x - \xo 6:2 \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:12; Oloko 5:16\x*” Obha̠ o̠pu̠r oloko wa̠ u̠b̠aram na̠ ogua̠n bho̠ ma̠a̠,
\v 3 “sa̠ ta̠ ebhon enigha̠ inyin, sa̠ inyin ta̠ od̠um iwewegh a̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ a̠de onon.”\x - \xo 6:3 \xt Oloko 5:16\x*
\v 4 Ro̠we̠de̠, o̠ni̠ ko orugh ado̠l ya̠ o̠gamame̠ni̠ rologi anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ ibhine d̠a̠ a̠kikiom na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ ekponom awa ma̠ ed̠ighom aru̠mu̠.
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ aru̠bana na̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ awa bho̠
\p 
\v 5 Aru̠bana, izuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ inyin i̠se̠n a̠de onon bho̠, ma̠ e̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu na̠ eb̠la̠ rologi d̠inyin, ma̠ enigha̠ awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin ta̠ oghila̠n Akrai̠st bho̠.
\v 6 O̠ni̠ ko ogir agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠bi̠gh inyin, ya̠a̠ igire kuma̠ agu̠o̠ aru̠bana ta̠ Akrai̠st ya̠ na̠ ebhin eb̠la̠ rologi d̠awa na̠ egir i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 7 Ibhine ma̠ onyen ologi ma̠ egir rogir d̠inyin, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ ogir na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ya̠a̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠.
\v 8 Iloghome ma̠a̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ asu̠o̠ ib̠eb̠i ogir d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, a̠d̠igh e̠bana, a̠d̠igh o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠bana.
\v 9 Inyin ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ aru̠bana, igire ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ awa. O̠ni̠ ko o̠pa awa. Iloghome ma̠a̠, Wa̠nwuna̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠nwuna̠ inyin sekina̠ awa, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠na o̠bhe̠l d̠o̠ ma̠ odi a̠kpon odi a̠gurumeni.
\s1 Eb̠la̠ o̠kpo̠ erorobhi ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠
\p 
\v 10 D̠a̠ okunugiom bho̠, bha̠ i̠mara gigiribh d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ ibom e̠mi̠ a̠limon d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 11 I̠lo̠gi̠ane̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ o̠kpo̠ erorobhi ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin orue o̠damaghan i̠karabh akpati̠an ta̠ Eru bho̠.
\v 12 Ezin bho̠, i̠yar uwia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ asi̠ na̠ ipulupul, ya̠a̠ na̠ owia̠n ogbo irileghom, na̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ra̠dila̠de i̠to̠, na̠ ogbo irileghom e̠mara̠nwunom azi̠m onon, na̠ a̠limon i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ re̠nai̠ny bho̠.
\v 13 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ibhine ma̠ eb̠la̠ o̠kpo̠ erorobhi ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ e̠kpaki̠an, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin orue o̠marama ma̠ o̠karabh a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ ma̠ igiel ta̠ a̠ru. Sa̠ igiel inyin na̠ o̠ne̠gi̠me̠ni̠ kabar kabar, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mara gigiribh.
\v 14 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠mara gigiribh ma̠ ebhin ya̠gia̠ga̠i ma̠ e̠kpo̠a ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠kara d̠a̠ eka̠ka̠gh d̠inyin, ma̠ ebhin a̠ghud̠um igielake̠ ma̠ eguri ma̠ agu̠o̠ ekpeke d̠a̠ ekpa̠kpa̠gh d̠inyin,
\v 15 ma̠ ebhin ebhiroma̠ o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ekima̠ bho̠ ma̠ e̠lo̠gi̠an agu̠o̠ agbaka.
\v 16 Wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠, i̠lo̠gi̠ane̠ ma̠ ekpeke ologi ima̠ra̠, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin orue o̠damaghan eb̠la̠ i̠so̠bh ya̠ na̠ emumor anya bho̠, ya̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠robhod̠i bho̠.
\v 17 Ibhine ma̠ itenemeni e̠mu̠gh ma̠ ezuoma̠ ka̠ eghoi e̠gham, ma̠ esibh ogidi e̠gham ta̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 18 Isiseinye ma̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere a̠siseiny ma̠ eb̠la̠ igiel d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠, ma̠ e̠mar ekpona̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ne, ma̠ esiseiny egboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 19 Isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ ami̠ nyen, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠, b̠o̠ka̠ igiel ami̠ i̠kpato̠n o̠nu̠ d̠ami̠, ami̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi agba ma̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ a̠mutiom.
\v 20 U̠tu̠n ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ o̠so̠n ami̠ ma̠ obhin a̠d̠ien ta̠ Akrai̠st o̠mara, sa̠ ami̠ od̠i ma̠ ikoli ma̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a. Isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ akpe̠ ami̠ ma̠ o̠gba bho̠.
\s1 Ipeleguma̠ wa̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠
\p 
\v 21 Od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ eloghom agu̠o̠ ami̠ od̠i, na̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠gir bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ iruom Atai̠siku̠s, umor ed̠ighologi d̠a̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠, na̠ o̠ni̠ogir igielake̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠,
\v 22 ma̠ oru ra̠ o̠gba agu̠o̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar od̠i onigha̠ inyin, na̠ o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ rologi d̠inyin.
\v 23 Ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, sekina̠ etula̠n na̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠a̠ ami̠ ya̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠.
\v 24 E̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ etula̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ etula̠n wa̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠.
